snippet.title: Teardown - Folkrace DLC
snippet.description:
Teardown's Folkrace DLC drops June 19 @ 2pm CET! Experience a high-octane single-player campaign with new maps, vehicles, and driving modes. Available on PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC. Race, wreck, and upgrade your way to victory!

Grab Teardown on Steam: https://steamcommunity.com/app/1167630
